ב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/27px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/41px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/54px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414021304\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.082 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.831 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 158/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 793/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4173/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.040/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5754880/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  741.020      1 -total\n 86.92%  644.096      4 תבנית:הערה\n 13.01%   96.371      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  4.25%   31.463      1 תבנית:אינפו\n  3.87%   28.653      1 תבנית:COL\n  1.99%   14.752      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n  1.59%   11.771      1 תבנית:וידאו\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:45796-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414021304 and revision id 814900. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
